  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I think that's how I preoccupied myself most of the time in those days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That-- that camp was-- there-- they-- they built another little camp after that, and so they split us sort of up to go to different places to work.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So it was a small camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I think there were like two barracks in the other camp, maybe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I used to be able to go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that's where the men-- a lot of-- mostly men were in that camp because they were working.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I remember [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] going-- going there with the groups, naturally.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You didn't go by yourself anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But since I was accepted in the camp, I was part of the group.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I used to be able to sneak in, and I felt very confident.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I-- I-- I guess maybe I wasn't scared of that part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because I remember, I snuck into that camp, and my father was in that camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And next to him was an old man, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and he taught me that song that-- he taught me a song that-- that I have-- I have performed quite a few times.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I did-- I-- I sang it in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I sang it at Yom HaShoah in-- in-- in-- in the  DP camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I also did it in 1989, I think, at Yom HaShoah here, in Los Angeles, which was a very hard thing for me to recollect it, because I-- I hadn't-- I hadn't written it down, and it's a monologue that lasts approximately four minutes.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it is not a little song.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a big story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is where I learned it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
